{
  "stem": "15991.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somehow, got some kind of education that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That, of course, was a very haphazard way to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGH] let's see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the war started in September.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with that, the bombing started as far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was at my sixteenth birthday in March.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was considered dangerous because I had not been in front of a tribunal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, there were tribunals for all the refugees in order to determine whether they were dangerous, half dangerous, or not at all dangerous-- ABC.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you were a C, you were OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since I was-- had just turned 16, there had been no time to put me in front of a tribunal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And consequently, one day, there was a police at the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said to my mother that he's come to take me away because they weren't sure whether I was dangerous or not.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so that was quite a shock for my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We quickly had to pack a tiny suitcase.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember packing a nail file, and he watched while we were packing this suitcase.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said, no nail files, no scissors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was taken to the local police station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember having to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a police woman came with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was impossible to go, [LAUGHS] because I was just so uptight having-- being-- ugh, having somebody come with me wherever I went.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, from there we were shipped to Liverpool into an enormous hall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I think it was a sports arena.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were hundreds and hundreds of refugees all in this arena.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember sitting next to a woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I looked at her, and I didn't like her looks.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
